 the University of Georgia."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","meanings":["Greek: the Lord gave graciously; whom Jehovah gave; whom Jehovah bestowed."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When John Claye was born in 1417, in Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, Sir John Claye Knt, was 22 and his mother, Emma Wood, was 22. He had at least 1 son. He died in Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1417–":"1417–Surnud","1417–Male":"1417–Surnud","1440–1532":"1440–1532","1395–1464":"1395–1464","1395–1417":"1395–1417","1532":"1532","1464":"1464","1440":"1440","1395":"1395","1417":"1417","Derbyshire, Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1417–":"1417–Kuollut","1417–Male":"1417–Kuollut","1440–1532":"1440–1532","1395–1464":"1395–1464","1395–1417":"1395–1417","1532":"1532","1464":"1464","1440":"1440","1395":"1395","1417":"1417","Derbyshire, Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1417–":"1417–Décédé","1417–Male":"1417–Décédé","1440–1532":"1440–1532","1395–1464":"1395–1464","1395–1417":"1395–1417","1532":"1532","1464":"1464","1440":"1440","1395":"1395","1417":"1417","Derbyshire, Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque John Claye est né en 1417, à Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Sir John Claye Knt, avait 22 ans et sa mère, Emma Wood, avait 22 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé à Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1417–":"1417–Verstorben","1417–Male":"1417–Verstorben","1440–1532":"1440–1532","1395–1464":"1395–1464","1395–1417":"1395–1417","1532":"1532","1464":"1464","1440":"1440","1395":"1395","1417":"1417","Derbyshire, Nottinghamshire, England":"